ainder of his sentence in a halfway house.]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<!-- do not apply CSS styles to this element! --><div class="pmc-paywall"><p
		class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "
> <em>Billboard</em>证实，被定罪的毒贩和洗钱头目 Demetrius “Big Meech” Flenory 已出狱，他在 2000 年代通过自己的唱片公司 BMF Entertainment 参与了说唱歌手<a  href="https://www.billboard.com/artist/jeezy/"  >Jeezy</a>和<a  href="https://www.billboard.com/artist/t-i/"  >TI</a>的早期职业生涯。</p><p
		class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "
>弗莱诺里因参与黑人黑手党家族犯罪团伙而被判犯有多项共谋犯罪和洗钱罪，并于 2008 年被判处 30 年监禁，于 10 月 15 日从佛罗里达州监狱获释，但必须服刑其余的人他的刑期（在监禁期间从 360 个月减至 292 个月）在中途之所。他预计将于 2026 年 1 月 27 日从中途宿舍获释，此后我们将受到监管释放。 </p><div class="injected-related-story // lrv-u-margin-tb-2 lrv-u-border-t-1 lrv-u-border-b-1 lrv-u-padding-t-050 lrv-u-padding-b-075 lrv-u-border-color-grey" ><div class="a-heading-border a-heading-border-background-color-grey a-heading-border-height-075 lrv-u-margin-b-075 lrv-u-margin-b-050@mobile-max"><h3 id="title-of-a-story" class="c-title  lrv-u-color-brand-primary a-font-primary-bold-s lrv-u-text-transform-uppercase lrv-u-padding-r-1 a-article-related-module-title a-article-related-module-title--color-brand-primary">有关的</h3></div><div class="o-card lrv-u-flex"><div class="c-lazy-image  lrv-u-height-100p"><div class="a-crop-3x2 a-crop-1x1@mobile-max lrv-u-height-100p"><img decoding="async" class="c-lazy-image__img lrv-u-background-color-grey-lightest lrv-u-width-100p lrv-u-display-block lrv-u-height-auto" src="https://www.billboard.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/02-50-Cent-Black-Mafia-Family-cr-Courtesty-Starz-Entertainment-billboard-1548-1632406437.jpg?w=237&#038;h=147&#038;crop=1" data-lazy-src="https://www.billboard.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/02-50-Cent-Black-Mafia-Family-cr-Courtesty-Starz-Entertainment-billboard-1548-1632406437.jpg?w=237&#038;h=147&#038;crop=1" alt="小德米特里厄斯·弗莱诺里 (Demetrius Flenory Jr)、50 Cent 和达芬奇" data-lazy-srcset="" data-lazy-sizes="" height="" width=""></div></div></div><div class="o-card__content lrv-u-flex lrv-u-flex-direction-column lrv-u-justify-content-center lrv-u-padding-lr-1 lrv-u-padding-lr-075@mobile-max"><div class="o_category "></div><div class="c_title "><h3 id="title-of-a-story" class="c-title  a-font-primary-medium-m lrv-u-padding-b-050 u-letter-spacing-0028@mobile-max"> 50 Cent 谈论在新的《BMF》中选角史努比狗狗，灵性和忽视…… </h3></div><time class="c-timestamp  a-font-primary-medium-xxs lrv-u-color-brand-primary lrv-u-order-100" datetime="00:00-YY-DD-MM"> 2021年9月23日</time></div></div></div><p
		class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "
> <em><a  href="https://www.tmz.com/2024/10/17/big-meech-special-condition-supervised-release-from-prison/"  rel="nofollow"  target="_blank"  >TMZ</a></em>最先报道了这一消息。</p><p
		class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "
>黑人黑手党家族于 20 世纪 80 年代中期在底特律成立，运作了大约 20 年，之后于 2005 年被美国缉毒局 (DEA) 捣毁，当时弗莱诺里、他的兄弟特里·弗莱诺里和 100 多名同谋被绳之以法。被捕并被指控犯有多项罪行。在法庭文件中，弗莱诺里被描述为“大规模跨州贩毒行动的领导者，拥有广泛的犯罪历史，包括之前因毒品、武器和袭击罪被定罪。”</p><p
		class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "
>最近， <a  href="https://www.billboard.com/artist/50-cent/"  >50 Cent</a>制作的 Starz 系列电视剧《BMF》记录了该团伙的兴衰，弗莱诺里的儿子小德米特里厄斯·弗莱诺里 (Demetrius Flenory Jr.) 在该剧中扮演了他的父亲。</p><p
		class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "
>对弗莱诺里被释放的消息发表评论的人包括说唱歌手<a  href="https://www.billboard.com/artist/sexyy-red/"  >性感红 (Sexyy Red)</a> ，他于周三（10 月 16 日）<a  rel="nofollow"  href="https://x.com/SexyyRed314_/status/1846630340380545343"  target="_blank"  >在推特上写道</a>：“欢迎回家派对@我是 trona 为 da freeski 表演。”同一天，Boosie Badazz 也在<a  href="https://x.com/BOOSIEOFFICIAL/status/1846648337229140089"  rel="nofollow"  target="_blank"  >推特</a>上庆祝，“欢迎回来#BIGMEECH #LEGEND。”周四（10 月 17 日），NBA 巨星勒布朗·詹姆斯<a  rel="nofollow"  href="https://x.com/KingJames/status/1846949695492415832"  target="_blank"  >在推特上写道</a>：“欢迎回家，大米奇！！”。</p></div> ]]>;</content:encoded><post-id xmlns="com-wordpress:feed-additions:1"> 1235805806</post-id></item><item><title> DJ Kaos 谈 J Balvin 秀的结束，为何 Feid 是他播放列表中的必备曲目 | Billboard LMW 35周年纪念演唱会</title><link/>https://www.billboard.com/video/dj-kaos-talks-looking-out-j-balvin-show-why-feid-is-a-must-have-on-his-playlist/<dc:creator><![CDATA[Stefanie Tanaka]]></dc:creator><pubDate> Sat, 19 Oct 2024 01:40:37 +0000</pubDate> <category><![CDATA[Media]]></category><category><![CDATA[Videos]]></category><category><![CDATA[Billboard]]></category><category><![CDATA[Billboard LMW 35th Anniversary Concert]]></category><guid ispermalink="false"> https://www.billboard.com/?post_type=pmc_top_video&amp;p=1235805826 </guid><description><![CDATA[DJ Kaos chatted with Billboard’s Jessica Roiz on the red carpet of the 35th Anniversary of Latin Music Week Concert. DJ Kaos conversó con Jessica Roiz de Billboard antes del concierto celebrando 35 años de Billboard’s Semana de Música Latina.]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<!-- do not apply CSS styles to this element! --><div class="pmc-not-a-paywall"><p
